title: Teenage.Mutant.Ninja.Turtles.Mutants.in.Manhattan-CODEX
description:
Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutants in Manhattan (c) Activision 


 Battle alongside your brothers through the sewers, subways, and
 streets of NYC to take down Shredder and Krang's evil organization,
 Foot by Foot. Unleash custom combat skills and powerful team combos
 to save Manhattan from the overwhelming dark forces growing in the
 shadows. Assemble your team in 4-player online co-op mode! Fight
 fan-favorite enemies like Bebop and Rocksteady!


 - Extract 
 - Burn or mount the .iso
 - Run setup.exe and install
 - Copy crack from CODEX dir to installdir
 - Play
